0:01:11.211,000 --> 0:01:13,000
That sticker wasn't there when I was a kid.

20
0:01:14.776,000 --> 0:01:15,000
But somewhere as the years passed,

21
0:01:16.694,000 --> 0:01:18,000
someone had the bright idea to put that sticker on the fruit.

22
0:01:19.575,000 --> 0:01:19,000
Why?

23
0:01:20.292,000 --> 0:01:21,000
So it could be easier for us

24
0:01:21.821,000 --> 0:01:22,000
to check out at the grocery counter.

25
0:01:23.558,000 --> 0:01:24,000
Well that's great,

26
0:01:24.651,000 --> 0:01:26,000
