93
0:04:35.415,000 --> 0:04:37,000
He just wanted a comfortable shower.

94
0:04:37.778,000 --> 0:04:39,000
Now, we've all been there,

95
0:04:39.941,000 --> 0:04:4,000
we just don't remember it.

