159
0:07:54.69,000 --> 0:07:56,000
Well, Steve noticed that

160
0:07:57.136,000 --> 0:07:57,000
and he said,

161
0:07:57.967,000 --> 0:07:59,000
"We're not going to let that happen to our product."

162
0:08:00.565,000 --> 0:08:01,000
